- Take list of IP addresses from web address as txt file.
- Better partitioning model, expressed as probability of partitions per
  hours, average duration, max nodes to filter in a given time, and so
  forth.
- Run as a deamon and get in touch with other nodes in order to simulate
  more partitioning models. For example a node may ask a few more to go
  into the same partition and so forth.
- Use proper command line options.
